name: Finger Print Sticker Book
description:
Finger Print Sticker Book by Emma Calder. These stickers are designed to be stuck anywhere, you feel like. I have seen them stuck on toilet doors, over the heads of the man and woman symbols.

The long thin book is 297 mm x 43 mm and contains 65 hand drawn stickers. Each book is unique, made up by hand by me, with slightly different combinations of the Finger Print Stickers on the recycled, thick paper covers. These books have been sold in places like The Tate Modern and Other Criteria. See header banner for the look of the covers. Please click to enlarge the image.
